These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, green, black, yellow
House: craftsman, townhouse, victorian, wooden
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, horse, rabbit
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, disaster, time-travel, horror
 1. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 2. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
 3. the person who likes orange is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the owner of the rabbit is the townhouse house##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5
 6. the craftsman house is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
 7. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the townhouse house##5
 9. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
10. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere between the person watching thriller movies and the person who likes orange##7
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
12. the wooden house is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
13. the person watching horror movies is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Color   | yellow    | green | black    | orange   |
| House   | craftsman | victorian | townhouse | wooden |
| Pet           | dog       | horse   | rabbit  | cat     |
| Movie-Genre     | thriller      | time-travel   | horror    | disaster    |

