The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, country, dubstep, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, chinese, indonesian, italian
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, rock-climbing, cooking, fishing
 1. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
 2. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
 3. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is the australian##1
 5. the fan of country is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 6. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
 7. the person drinking 7up is somewhere between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the australian##7
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
10. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
11. the chinese is the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage          | iced-tea   | hot-chocolate       | 7up    | mirinda      |
| Music-Genre   | house | trance | country         | dubstep   |
