There are 4 different nationalities: german, polish, russian, spanish
4 different games are played: bridge, monopoly, mah-jongg, domino
 1. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
 2. the person playing domino is somewhere between the person who likes pink and the person who's birthday is in october##7
 3. the person who likes lavender is the polish##1
 4. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
 5. the german is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
 6. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 7. the person who likes white is not the person who's birthday is in july##6
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is not the person who likes coral##6
 9. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
10. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
11. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
12. the russian is the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Color           | coral | pink | lavender | white |
| Birthday   | january        | february    | july    | october    |
| Nationality   | german        | spanish   | polish   | russian         |
| Game           | monopoly          | bridge       | domino   | mah-jongg           |

