The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, satire
 1. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 2. the cape-cod house is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not the person watching crime movies##6
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 8. the tower house is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's sport is skateboarding##7
 9. the tower house is the person watching crime movies##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
11. the townhouse house is not the person watching crime movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |        3        |      4       |
