 5. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
 6. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
 8. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 9. the person who's sport is badminton is somewhere between the person eating eggplant and the person eating tomato##7
10. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
11. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
12. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
13. the person who's hobby is board-games is not the person playing snooker##6
14. the person who's hobby is photography is not the person eating onion##6
