 2. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the person eating corn##5
 4. the person eating banana is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
 6. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere between the person who growsiris and the person who growsbegonia##7
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the person who growsiris##6
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person eating banana##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Hobby         | chess      | cooking   | sudoku   | puzzles       |
| Birthday   | march | april    | july | september       |
| Food   | radish  | broccoli | banana   | corn     |
| Flower         | iris   | poppy    | begonia   | amaryllis |

