.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, poker, canasta, whist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, pop, country, indie
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, hiking, reading
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, tennis, badminton, water-polo
 1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the fan of folk##5
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is badminton##2
 4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 5. the fan of pop is not the person who's sport is tennis##6
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the fan of country##5
 7. the person playing whist is somewhere between the person playing scrabble and the fan of indie##7
 8. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
 9. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
10. the fan of pop is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
11. the person playing scrabble is the fan of country##1
12. the fan of country is not the person who's sport is badminton##6

