.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
House: wooden, townhouse, victorian, tower
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, american, indonesian, nigerian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, punk, indie, electronic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rowing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 2. the indonesian is the victorian house##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is the fan of electronic##1
 4. the fan of indie is between the tower house and the townhouse house##2
 5. the polish is somewhere to the right of the townhouse house##5
 6. the fan of folk is somewhere between the indonesian and the wooden house##7
 7. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the american##5
 8. the fan of folk is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the american is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
10. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
12. the polish is somewhere to the right of the townhouse house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| House   | tower      | victorian     | townhouse   | wooden    |
| Nationality     | nigerian | indonesian   | american | polish |
| Music-Genre     | electronic        | indie     | folk  | punk      |
| Sport   | rowing       | water-polo | cricket   | skiing    |

 